    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The switching functions and data transfer between the tractor terminal or ISO control box and the machine are operated via the ISOBUS. Specifically tilling the site and reacting to deviating field forms or soil compositions is possible through ISOBUS communication. With GPS, various sensors and management systems are provided with the necessary information in order to control the machine optimally."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "ISOBUS functionality via IsoMatch"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Tractors without their own ISO terminal can work as ISO tractors with the IsoMatch control box."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Driving speed, RPM and GPS signal on IsoMatch"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If speed is not measured on the (trailed) machine, but via the tractor, the speed sensor or the adapter cable is to be connected to the IsoMatch to capture the speed signal from the tractor electronics. A special cable set is required for this."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See paragraph \u00bbDirectly to the ISO 11786 in cab tractor connection in the tractor cabin\u00ab on page 144."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The same applies for the PTO shaft RPM. The extra sensor is available for this purpose."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The GPS signal can also be used via the RS 232 on the control box. This is required for the GEOCONTROL functionality."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae Also, refer to the manual that comes with your control box."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Adapting non-ISO tractors with IsoMatch power cable set"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If the tractor does not have an ISOBUS communication, it can be added with the IsoMatch power cable set."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Hereafter, your tractor is entirely ISOBUS ready, and you can connect and operate the machine with the IsoMatch control box."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The driving speed of your tractor (or your trailed machine) is transmitted via the ISOBUS to the IsoMatch."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The \"IM Tellus Input\" cable, supplied as a standard item, can be used for other connections."
    }
  ]
}

{
  "page_number": 33,
  "items": [
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Getting familiar with the machine"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "The control box"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The working method and work performance of the IsoMatch control box are described in this user's manual."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch universal ISOBUS terminal"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Many functions and programmes on one control box"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The divided colour screen has a flexible division to:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Operate 2 programmes or functions simultaneously on screen, e.g. the main screen of your machine and a separate operating program. This can be done without having to switch."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Operate all keys directly on the touch screen."
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Instruction booklet of the terminal in the correct language on screen."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Check the following by camera in the cabin while working:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 a specific point on the machine,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 the crop,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 or the vicinity."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "33"
    }
  ]
}

{
