      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Camera screen (Camera is optional)"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Status bar for time, GPS signal strength and driving direction"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Save and read:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Documents."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Tractor data."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Field data."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Work particulars of various ISO machines."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Client particulars."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "With the main switch on the upper left in the red extension, you can switch the control box on and off."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Press the button for at least 1 sec."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Always switch off the control box when you leave the tractor."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If the box is engaged, unintended functions can be activated while you are in the danger area. Moreover, the control box uses power, as a result of which the tractor battery could be flattened."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "After starting up, the screen with the last (two) selected applications appears."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Compact and complete"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch Go, as a handy and more compact variant of the doublescreen version, offers complete ISO control with all functions. Besides the smaller dimension with the single screen, the number of USB connections and the absence of Wlan/Wifi constitutes the biggest difference."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Many additional functions."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The latest developments in ISOBUS communication between tractor and implement and ease-of-use are all incorporated into the IsoMatch Tellus GO."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Connect the ISOBUS tractor via IM Tellus 9-point in Cab cable"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If your tractor is provided with a full ISOBUS connection, a connection with the 9-pins in Cab cable between your tractor and the IsoMatch Tellus GO control box is sufficient."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Other connections are made via the \"Input IM Tellus\" cable, supplied as a standard item."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Quick menu navigation with the scroll wheel and additional keys"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "A scroll wheel on the upper right of the box makes it easy to scroll"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "through the menu."
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
