    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Scroll-wheel navigation"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "34"
    }
  ]
}

{
  "page_number": 35,
  "items": [
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch Grip"
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Getting familiar with the machine"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The IsoMatch Grip accessory is a control unit on which most of the implement functions used can be operated centrally with one handle. This is available in addition to the ISOBUS terminal such as the IsoMatch."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Handle control"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "While working attention and visibility is often required to follow the work process. By locating the control buttons on the handle by touch, it will enable you to keep your eyes on the driving system control and remain focussed while driving."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If operating buttons can be located by the sense of touch reaction speed can be increased and operating mistakes avoided."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "44 functions under 11 buttons"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The IsoMatch Grip has 11 function buttons and one selector that are operated with the thumb and under which there are 44 functions."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "35"
    }
  ]
}

