      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch terminal on an ISO tractor"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If you use the IsoMatch control box with a tractor manufactured with the ISOBUS communication system, you can connect it with the supplied CAN cable to a standard tractor CAN connection."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Connect the side of the cable to which 1 plug is attached to the tractor CAN connection."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Connect the side of the cable to which 2 plugs are attached to control box connections."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch terminal on a NONISO tractor If you use the IsoMatch control box with a tractor that is not equipped with the ISOBUS communication system, an extra cable set is needed. This cable set is included in the order or can be supplied via"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "your dealer."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "With the non-ISO adaptor cable set, you can equip any tractor type with a full ISOBUS communication system."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The fixing materials and the assembly instructions are delivered with the IsoMatch control box."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See also paragraph \u00bbIsoMatch universal ISOBUS terminal\u00ab on page 33 and the description on page 142."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Connect the cables so that you can work safely."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If you want to use the GEOCONTROL functionality, you should use a localisation system on the tractor. If you mount a separate GPS receiver on the tractor, you should connect the plug to the rear on the control box. Then switch on the appropriate external signal as described in"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The instruction manual of the software."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "See also the user's manual of the"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 ISO control box,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 tractor,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 and GPS."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "GPS signal for GEOCONTROL"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Before first use"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "41"
    }
  ]
}

