{
  "page_number": 49,
  "items": [
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Tractor provisions"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "power lift"
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Stabiliser chain"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Electrical installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Hydraulic system of the tractor"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Before first use"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Working with the machine requires a tractor that at least meets the following requirements:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 sufficient carrying and lifting capacity and engine power, \uf0ae see paragraph \u00bbTechnical specifications\u00ab on page 36,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 correct type and power lift that can be set well, with linkage frame (optional extras) if required for tractors with power lift of Cat. 3 / 4,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 ISOBUS communication system and ISOBUS plug attachment or,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 assembled ISO control terminal to operate the spreader."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 GPS for GEOCONTROL functionality."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The tractor must be equipped with a Cat. 2 three point power lift or with linkage frame (optional extras) for tractors with power lift of Cat. 3 / 4. Easy control of top link and lower link adjustment is important. This system is used for several machine settings."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The tractor must be equipped with stabiliser rods or chains for:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 preventing lateral machine movements and"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 being able to select the correct position of the machine relative to the tractor."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Lighting"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "A stop contact is required for the lights."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Control system"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "To operate the spreader, you need a connection for the ISOBUS plug. \uf0ae See chapter \u00bbIsoMatch terminal on a NON-ISO tractor\u00ab on page 41."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The tractor must have a valve to operate the machine accessories."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "This number can increase, depending on the accessories selected:"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Required hydraulic valves"
    },
    {
