{
  "page_number": 78,
  "items": [
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "To be done before spreading"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Test the left and right spreading patterns"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "INDICATION"
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The left and right spreading discs must spread the same volumes of fertiliser to ensure good distribution. Check this every year!"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "This test describes a working width of 24 metres. You are of course free to run the test for a different working width. Divide the buckets at equal distances along the working width."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Operation"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Switch the tractor off, remove the key from the ignition and engage the parking brake of the tractor."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Disconnect the left spreading disc by sliding the connector to he left. Secure the connector with a lock clip."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Search the correct discharge position to spread over 24 metres in the best comparable fertiliser, seeds or granules (online) spreading chart and set the handle accordingly."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See paragraph \u00bbDischarge point\u00ab on page 65 and the foreword of the spreading chart book."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Fit the coupling shaft to the correct attachment point of the central gearbox as indicated in the associated spreading chart."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See paragraph \u00bbCoupling shaft connection point\u00ab on page 64."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Check the height of the spreader (height of the spreading disc = 75 cm above the troughs) ."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Place the grids in the troughs."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Place trough 1 in the middle of the tractor tracks."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Place the other troughs 4 metres to the right of the tractor tracks."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "INDICATION Position the troughs horizontally with a spirit level!"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "78"
    }
  ]
}

{
  "page_number": 79,
  "items": [
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
