    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "You will most likely get into contact with the fertiliser and other material you may wish to spread while filling, adjusting and testing the spreader. Wear protective clothing and safety gloves, read the safety instructions provided by the supplier and follow their directions. Contact with these materials could cause physical harm."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Be careful that nothing gets jammed"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "It is easy for parts to get jammed while adjusting and checking the spreader."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Work safely while checking and adjusting:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 switching off the electronic control system,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 switch the tractor off and remove the key from the ignition,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 engage the parking brake of the tractor,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 wait for all machine parts to come to a standstill before you start with the adjustments,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 wear protective clothing, such as safety gloves and shoes,"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 carefully follow the instructions given."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Friction with these materials could cause physical injury."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The agitator axle is equipped with a plastic seal to prevent fertiliser granule loss along the agitator axle. The seal must be replaced every season, as well as after every 100 operational hours. Only work on a clean machine with an empty hopper."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Set the fine application handle to the normal dosing setting."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Start the tractor and engage the control box."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Activate the empty hopper function."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae Please refer to the software instruction manual"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Wait until both actuators are completely extended and the dosing units are completely open."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Place the machine on the ground or on firm supports on a firm, level ground."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Switch the electronic control system and the tractor off, remove the key from the ignition and engage the parking brake of the tractor."
    }
  ]
}

{
  "page_number": 141,
