    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Open the sieves with the included attachment and deposit it."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Remove the agitator from the agitator axle."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Support the fertiliser bearing ring through a dosing opening so that it will not drop."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Remove the 3 fastening bolts from the seal rings."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Remove the metal seal rings."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Check the condition of the agitator axle."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Replace the fertiliser sealing ring."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Put the metal seal rings back in position."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Put the 3 fastening bolts back in place."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "TIP You can let go of the plastic bearing ring again after the first fastening bolt has been put in place."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf034 Put the agitator back into the agitator axle."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Check the connections as described in"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae paragraph \u00bbChecking and setting the dosing mechanism\u00ab on page 133."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
