{
  "page_number": 143,
  "items": [
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch Tellus GO control box"
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "ISOBUS tractor connection"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Input IM Tellus with ISO11786 In cab connection"
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": "Input IM Tellus with ISO11786 In cab connection"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Conversion to non-ISO tractor with IsoMatch power"
    },
    {
      "type": "PictureItem",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Accessories"
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Compact and complete"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch Go, as a handy and more compact variant of the doublescreen version, offers complete ISO control with all functions. Besides the smaller dimension with the single screen, the number of USB connections and the absence of Wlan/Wifi constitutes the biggest difference."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Many additional functions."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The latest developments in ISOBUS communication between tractor and implement and ease-of-use are all incorporated into the IsoMatch Tellus GO."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "A scroll wheel on the upper right of the box and an additional keyboard make menu navigation easy."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Connect the ISOBUS tractor via IM Tellus 9-point in Cab cable"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If your tractor is provided with a full ISOBUS connection, a connection with the 9-pins in Cab cable between your tractor and the IsoMatch Tellus GO control box is sufficient."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Other connections are made via the \"Input IM Tellus\" cable, supplied as a standard item."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Connect the ISOBUS tractor via IM Tellus 9-point in Cab cable"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If your tractor is provided with a complete ISOBUS connection, a connection with the 9-pins in Cab cable between your tractor and the IsoMatch control box is sufficient."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Other connections are made via the \"Input IM Tellus\" cable, supplied as a standard item."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "Input IM Tellus with ISO11786 In cab connection"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "A connection set is supplied as a standard item with the IsoMatch for:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 ISO 11786 In cab"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 lights and ignition"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Tractor CAN (optional plug specific to the tractor required)"
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\u00b7 Video input."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch power cable set for non-ISO tractors"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "If the tractor does not have an ISOBUS communication, it can be added with the IsoMatch power cable set."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Hereafter, your tractor is entirely ISOBUS ready, and you can connect and operate the machine with the IsoMatch control box."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The \"Input IM Tellus\" cable, supplied as a standard item, can be used for other connections."
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "143"
    }
  ]
}

