    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "To complement the GEOCONTROL functions an optically guided steering"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "instrument will assist you in finding and keeping the A-B line during various activities."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "DGPS driven steering"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The upper and middle section shows the DGPS driven steering while spraying and for other treatments, where close monitoring of the pass is required."
    },
    {
      "type": "SectionHeaderItem",
      "text": "GEOCONTROL Section Activity"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "At the bottom of the display you will see the enabled and disabled sections displayed."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See the website www.isomatchshop.com"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "The latest development in ISOBUS communication is an extension to the IsoMatch terminal for tractors which cannot give any own locational information. The GPS antenna with DGPS accuracy allows satellite navigation for field-specific section control, variable dosing and field registration."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See the website www.isomatchshop.com"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "Connection with local Wireless Internet and IsoMatch. With IsoMatch Wireless, you can easily connect the IsoMatch Tellus (GO) to any wireless network. Think of hot spot, home network, etc."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See the website www.isomatchshop.com"
    },
    {
      "type": "TextItem",
      "text": "IsoMatch Eye is an accessory for better visibility, day and night. The camera can be connected to the IsoMatch Tellus and IsoMatch Tellus GO terminal."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "\uf0ae See the website www.isomatchshop.com"
