      "text": "3. The seller is also responsible for intentional and gross neglect caused by him/her or by someone under his/her supervision for so far as responsibility has not been determined under point 1 yet. Liability for his/her own neglect in terms of simple neglect by his/her legal representatives or on his behalf by people under his/her supervision excluded, will the requirements of point 2 remain valid."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "4. Insofar as there is liability in terms of points 2 and 3, the extent thereof is limited to normal remuneration for damage incurred."
    },
    {
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "5. The above regulations under 1 to 4 can be applied to any liability with the conclusion of the agreement. These stipulations are limited with retroactive effect to damages based on this legal title."
    }
